{"type":"answer","id":28939,"parentType":"question","parentId":7033,"uid":4341,"contents":"志问志答写了两个答案~<br>\n<br>\n1. 老蟾师还是不倒高了，续da命，拜大肚肚维尼佛吧~<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/g0VMEWU.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/g0VMEWU.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/g0VMEWU.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n2，老蟾师如果执意倒高，那么在哭墙前，老蟾师应该佩戴<b>基巴帽（כִּפָּה‎），</b>泽可被称为以泽列民；维一的坏处就是会因此和法轮王蟾生矛盾，然后被蟾扶走去修建“近”字塔。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/QXhTVgH.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QXhTVgH.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/QXhTVgH.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-20","agreeCount":11,"discussionCount":0}